<exercise checkit-seed="0004" checkit-slug="M4" checkit-title="Finding a matrix inverse">
  <statement>
      <p>Show how to find the inverse of the matrix <m>C=\left[\begin{array}{cccc}
1 &amp; 4 &amp; 4 &amp; -1 \\
1 &amp; 5 &amp; 5 &amp; -1 \\
1 &amp; 2 &amp; 3 &amp; 2 \\
1 &amp; 1 &amp; 2 &amp; 3
\end{array}\right]</m>.</p>
  </statement>
  <answer>
      <me>C^{-1}=\left[\begin{array}{cccc}
4 &amp; -3 &amp; -1 &amp; 1 \\
-1 &amp; 2 &amp; -4 &amp; 3 \\
0 &amp; -1 &amp; 4 &amp; -3 \\
-1 &amp; 1 &amp; -1 &amp; 1
\end{array}\right]</me>
  </answer>
</exercise>
